pray Insectos Fuera cada pocas semanas, ya que no hay ning\u00fan tipo de conservante en la mezcla.\nFuente Andrea Butje\nNos encantar\u00eda que nos contases tus experiencias preparando esta sinergia de aceites esenciales e Hidrolato de Menta y su efectividad para ahuyentar insectos.\n\u00a1Feliz fin de semana!", "language": null, "image": "https://oshadhi.es/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/picadura-300x225-1.jpeg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://www.facebook.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://twitter.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://www.instagram.com/oshadhiespana/", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh9UPZpidfNhcmn4rmcyuXQ", "https://oshadhi.es/?cms_block=localizacion", "mailto:info@oshadhi.es", "#contact-form-popup", "/politica-de-privacidad/", "mailto:lopd@oshadhi.es", "/politica-de-privacidad", "mailto:info@oshadhi.es", "https://www.facebook.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://twitter.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://www.instagram.com/oshadhiespana/", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh9UPZpidfNhcmn4rmcyuXQ", "https://goo.gl/maps/PAfhRqCznmc6efPH6", "https://oshadhi.es/contacto/", "https://oshadhi.es/lista-de-deseos/", "https://oshadhi.es/carrito/", "https://www.facebook.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://twitter.com/OshadhiEspana", "https://www.instagram.com/oshadhiespana/", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh9UPZpidfNhcmn4rmcyuXQ", "https://oshadhi.es/", "https://oshadhi.es/?cms_block=menu-category-7", "/tienda/aceites/", "/tienda/aceites/esenciales/", "/tienda/aceites/sinergias/", "/tienda/bases-vegetales/", "/tienda/bases-vegetales/bases-vegetales-aceites/", "/tienda/bases-vegetales/macerados/", "/tienda/bases-vegetales/mantecas/", "/tienda/ayurveda/", "/tienda/ayurveda/marma/", "/tienda/ayurveda/sama-dosha/", "/tienda/belleza/", "/tienda/belleza/cocteles-de-aloe/", "/tienda/belleza/corporal/", "/tienda/belleza/facial/", "/tienda/perfume/", "/tienda/perfume/ambiente/", "/tienda/perfume/eau-de-toilette/", "/tienda/perfume/jojobas/", "/tienda/hidrolaterapia/", "/tienda/libros-